      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 01:55:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着存栏量减少，中国陷入困境的养猪户看到了好转</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-s-distressed-pig-farmers-eye-turnaround-as-herd-shrinks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国农民的养殖生猪存栏量为2020年以来最少，这为该行业在经历多年亏损后即将迎来持续盈利带来了希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-s-distressed-pig-farmers-eye-turnaround-as-herd-shrinks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 01:53:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券牛市推动中国信贷收益率跌至历史新低</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-s-credit-yields-drop-to-record-lows-on-bond-bull-run</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着投资者在流动性充沛的金融体系中大量购买公司债券以提高回报，中国的本地信贷收益率已跌至历史最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-s-credit-yields-drop-to-record-lows-on-bond-bull-run</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 01:04:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
